title: Quitting YouTube, Hair Loss, Hate Comments, and Counseling ft. Dani Austin
description:
Today, we have an OG guest, Dani Austin. We are talking about work boundaries, hair loss due to stress, therapy, and so much more.

Want to send Jeanine a message?  You can do that here: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy by clicking "Message."
